---
title: Saucy Beef Tacos with Seasoned Rice and Feta
description: Get ready for your new go-to taco night recipe, because these saucy handhelds are sure to be a hit! They're jam-packed with spices, served with smoky seasoned rice and topped off with creamy feta cheese and lime crema.
